      "span_text": "According to  , educators have tended to adopt these new technologies within their existing teaching paradigms, replicating a stubbornly teacherdirected practice that focuses on content delivery rather than leveraging the unique affordances of mobile computing to redefine the possibilities of learning and assessment activities in the mobile era."
